{"tid":1853292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FBI通緝中國間諜 Yanqung Ye 涉扮學生偷生物化學研究成果","createTime":"2020-01-31T01:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T02:20:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf747fb2004dc4ebaf31ba3b114905fe7f8c830","tid":1853292,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NBUVDjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNBUVDjy.png&h=a6002677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"028c92fe0946f1cfa770e19a0e923b39046c8524","tid":1853292,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:32:38.000Z","msg":"之前嗰化學教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個窮科學家移民美國的夢幻故事<br />\n<br />\n早兩天在這兒貼過，震驚全球學術界，哈佛大學化學及化學生物學系系主任、著名科學家 Charles Lieber 涉嫌欺騙美國政府關於其與中国之間的來往的新聞。Lieber 今天獲准以一百萬美元保釋，其間與妻子須交出旅遊證件，並不得接觸武汉科技大学、北京大学、中国科学院的人員。<br />\n<br />\n美國化學學會 Chemical &amp; Engineering News 以及哈佛大學學生報 Harvard Crimson 的報導，對其涉嫌犯罪行為有更深入的描述。最令我注目的一點，是 Lieber 於未得到哈佛大學校方同意下，與武汉科技大学簽約，成立「哈佛 - 武汉科技大学納米研究中心」，並成為執行主管，讓武汉科技大学的科學家每年花兩個月時間到訪哈佛（即係大開中門畀人偷野！），然後對哈佛的調查人員指稱武汉科技大学未經其同意使用哈佛校名及校徽：<br />\n<br />\n//Lieber allegedly signed a contract that obligated Harvard to become part of a cooperative research program that allowed WUT scientists to visit the university up to two months each year. The complaint says he did not inform university officials of the agreement, which was for &ldquo;advanced research and development of nano wire-based lithium-ion batteries with high performance for electric vehicles.&rdquo;//<br />\n<br />\n//In one instance, Lieber established a joint Harvard-WUT lab on nanotechnology &mdash; for which he served as Executive Director &mdash; despite lacking the authority to contract on behalf of Harvard. When University administrators confronted Lieber about the lab and his affiliations in China, Lieber told them that WUT was using the Harvard name without his knowledge, according to the affidavit.//<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://cen.acs.org/research-integrity/misconduct/Harvard-chemist-Charles-Lieber-charged/98/i5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcen.acs.org%2Fresearch-integrity%2Fmisconduct%2FHarvard-chemist-Charles-Lieber-charged%2F98%2Fi5&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7cb1f0cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cen.acs.org/research-integrity/misconduct/Harvard-chemist-Charles-Lieber-charged/98/i5</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2020/1/29/lieber-federal-charges/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecrimson.com%2Farticle%2F2020%2F1%2F29%2Flieber-federal-charges%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e64a3688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2020/1/29/lieber-federal-charges/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFg5f6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFg5f6Z.png&h=2ee25c4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67759f63d692858753f0b1057e29a1279bfc76ca","tid":1853292,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"應該是鬼佬肉便器，上完床再俾錢收賣鬼佬"},{"pid":"e4a24bf7ad56fbb34fec7d70a7c7b5f8869758b8","tid":1853292,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"支那福建賤畜"},{"pid":"81dee04a1559e87963293eeb082c29030b75fcbf","tid":1853292,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:33:00.000Z","msg":"【疫情展望】手足做好防護措施，去到 Phase II. 就仆街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/artyfjU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/artyfjU</a>"},{"pid":"0c8c4378f6ddd86523a1ce4d937cb083af76779d","tid":1853292,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:39:15